---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contributing" description="How to contribute to the AI-Me specification and tooling.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Contributing</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      AI-Me is an open specification. Contributions are welcome.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-10">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Ways to contribute</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Report issues</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              Found a problem with the spec, website, or tooling? <a href="https://github.com/aselims/ai-me/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-600 underline dark:text-primary-400">Open an issue</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Propose changes</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              Have an idea for the spec? Start a discussion on GitHub, then submit a pull request.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Add examples</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              Contribute discovery manifest examples for new site types and use cases.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5 dark:border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Build tooling</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              Create validators, generators, or client libraries in your language of choice.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Getting started</h2>
        <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <li><strong>1.</strong> Fork the <a href="https://github.com/aselims/ai-me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-600 underline dark:text-primary-400">repository</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>2.</strong> Read the <a href="https://github.com/aselims/ai-me/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-600 underline dark:text-primary-400">CONTRIBUTING.md</a> for detailed guidelines.</li>
          <li><strong>3.</strong> Make your changes and submit a pull request.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Guidelines</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <li>• Follow the existing code style and conventions.</li>
          <li>• Keep pull requests focused — one change per PR.</li>
          <li>• Spec changes should include updated examples and JSON Schema.</li>
          <li>• All contributions are licensed under Apache-2.0.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Code of conduct</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          We follow the <a href="https://www.contributor-covenant.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-600 underline dark:text-primary-400">Contributor Covenant</a> code of conduct. Be respectful, constructive, and inclusive.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
